cleaned_text: Searching for a holistic, integrative health care provider? Do the following: - Click on the categories below to see providers with listings for those services. They are ordered by the most recent placement. - Use the 'SEARCH' field for last names, not types of provider, practice names, etc. - Use the 'ADVANCED SEARCH' function below the FIND LISTINGS button for types of business, locations, etc. - Use the 'SORT' options under the categories of providers to sort the listings alphabetically within each category.
